{"tid":867541,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想問佢拎電話（女生角度）","createTime":"2018-10-18T17:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T20:20:38.000Z","uid":82920,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7e6d97bd7610a90d0a810aeb189556a0ecc2b9","tid":867541,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"話說今日1點半幾係九龍塘上車，見到個好吸睛既男仔，<br />\n點知下一站就有位，仲要咁岩係佢隔離，<br />\n就坐埋去啦<br />\n因為我不嬲拍羞唔敢望靚仔，所以佢訓緊覺我都唔敢偷望佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （可能其實唔靚仔tim haha）<br />\n但就係唔知有種氣場咁⋯⋯<br />\n然後佢突然唔再訓，望左一望我部手機<br />\n跟住就自己變得好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解係想認識佢個程度係好想間佢拎電話<br />\n完全覺得自己傻左<br />\n一直搭到調景嶺一齊落就個心就一直笠笠亂咁耐⋯⋯<br />\n一落車即奔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話：如果個男仔keep住望你係有意思定覺得你好7⋯⋯<br />\n我知架啦別ff太多呀ma<br />\n純粹想問有無絲打都試過呢個感覺<br />\n嗚<br />\n如果你見到個po就好<br />\n<br />\n成世都未試過有呢個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b853f97b9ae7053021e7d2d315abf4c0987041","tid":867541,"uid":190167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"覺得你柒 唔會keep住望你  完"},{"pid":"43317c2dcd1229730ed0e1ad7aef713dc0c0c992","tid":867541,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"吸你老母睛"},{"pid":"65ea317e4f3411a5ceb4cd58c28922d810d61670","tid":867541,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:07:41.000Z","msg":"keep住望你一定有意思"},{"pid":"9bbcc5aa3b961c4aa7dfaf14b083823bcae6e228","tid":867541,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"人地有女朋友  毒撚唔好諗咁多等人炒你牌仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec3d16d526acc0c24bc7804bc0b204303509c2b","tid":867541,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"樓主照下鏡就知佢點諗"},